The above petition invokes the celestial officials, generals, and hosts of the preceding sections, each in their full assembly, to act on behalf of your disciple [Name], to erase their name from the death ledger, to inscribe their name in the register of the living, to grant them a lifespan of 120 years, to augment their years and prolong their life, and to perpetually safeguard their boundless fortune. Hasten, hasten, in accordance with the statutes and ordinances of the Most High Lord Lao.

