The above petition invokes the celestial officials, generals, and hosts of the preceding sections, each in their full assembly, to act on behalf of your disciple [Name] throughout the heavens, earth, and the bureaus of the Three Officials of Water and Earth, in the realms of adversity, to sequentially seek and retrieve your disciple’s [Name] three hun and seven po souls, nine lives and seven registers, form and shadow, essence and radiance, spirit and darkness, and to restore them within the body, ensuring their completeness and authenticity, reviving the hun and restoring the po, extending life through calamitous years. Hasten, hasten, in accordance with the statutes and ordinances.

