One Lord of the Gate of the Keepers of Destiny, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of Deliverance from Peril, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of Severing Repeated Afflictions, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of Longevity, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of the Northern Controller of Destiny, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of the Minister of Works, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of the Registrars, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of the Filial and Spring Clerks, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of the Recorders, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of the Seven Prisons Clerks, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
One Lord of the Gate of the Examiners of Life, with one hundred twenty officials and generals;
